|-----------|-------|-------|--------|
| Naming (15%) | 14/20 | -1 | `fail_on_dirty_tree` naming is non-obvious (convention is `skip_on_dirty`); `_clean_action` is vague; but `STORY_ENTRY_COUNT`, `get_server_log_path()` are good |
| Error Handling (20%) | 15/20 | -1 | `_clean_action` regex has no exception handling; `server.log_path` access lacks hasattr guard; server.stop swallows exceptions silently |
| Type Safety (20%) | 13/20 | -1 | `get_server_log_path()` missing `hasattr` guard; `_clean_action` implicit Any; type coverage incomplete |
| Architecture (20%) | 12/20 | -1 | Evidence utils hardcoded "worldarchitectai" regression; 21 copy-paste lines not architecture; but log path abstraction and invariant refactor are genuinely good |
| Test Coverage (15%) | 15/20 | -1 | Parallel runner is harness not tests; net effect of additions/removals is moderate; no unit test for new method |
| Documentation (10%) | 12/20 | 0 | Good shell comments, updated docstrings; unchanged |

